@startuml ebu_PlugIt

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor<<API>> LightBlue
  BackgroundColor<<Client>> LightGreen
}

[GitHub Repository] as Repo
[Analysis Client] as Client <<Client>>
[Google Gemini API] as GeminiAPI <<API>>
[Rate Limit Handler] as RateHandler
[Token Usage Monitor] as TokenMonitor

Repo --> Client : Repository content
Client --> GeminiAPI : API requests
GeminiAPI --> Client : API responses
Client --> RateHandler : 429 errors
RateHandler --> Client : Retry logic
Client --> TokenMonitor : Usage data

note right of GeminiAPI
  Rate Limit:
  - Model: gemini-2.0-flash
  - Quota: generate_content_free_tier_input_token_count
  - HTTP Status: 429 (Too Many Requests)
end note

note bottom of RateHandler
  - Implements backoff strategy
  - Retry delays: 10-12 seconds
end note

note bottom of TokenMonitor
  Tracks token consumption
  to prevent quota violations
end note

@enduml